\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6230726 , the space station or carrier battle group represents the \'93cities and towns\'94 where
 everyone docks, particularly when they first start playing the game.  Rather than squirreling away new players in their own bay where no one else can see them like EVE-Online does (The bay in EVE\rquote 
s space station is not only isolated, but is exactly the sa
me regardless of the size of your ship!), we want to allow players to see their ships right along side of other player (and non-player) ships.  The space-station is the BEST place to see the other ships in the game and to show of OUR designs (ship models,
